trans-unit.source: Provides a glyph for an <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"></xref> to display when the activity it is associated with is set to read only at design time.
trans-unit.target: Zawiera symbol <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"> </xref> wyświetlany, gdy działanie jest skojarzony z ustawiono odczytać tylko w czasie projektowania.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ReadOnlyActivityGlyph"></xref> class.
Returns the bounds for the glyph on the specified <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Zwraca granice dla symbolu na określonym <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ActivityDesigner"></xref> with which the glyph is associated.

<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to indicate whether the glyph appears on the activity designer surface; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Rectangle"></xref> that represents the bounds for the glyph.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Rectangle"> </xref> reprezentujący granice dla symbolu.

trans-unit.source: designer contains a null reference ( in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: designerzawiera odwołanie o wartości null ( w języku Visual Basic).

trans-unit.target: Wykonuje wszelkie zadania wymagane do renderowania symbolu na powierzchni projektowej działania.

trans-unit.target: <xref href="System.Drawing.Graphics"> </xref> Do wypełnienia i rysowanie zadania.

trans-unit.source: Gets the priority setting for the glyph on the activity designer surface.
trans-unit.target: Pobiera ustawienia priorytetu dla symbolu na powierzchni projektowej działania.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.ShadowGlyph.Priority%2A> always returns the integer value associated with <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerGlyph.LowestPriority?displayProperty=fullName>.
